• For our energy related services, competitors vary by locality and type of services provided, with competition coming
from national, regional and local service providers. Competition is based on a number of factors, including safety, quality,
performance, reliability, service, price, response time and, in some cases, breadth of service offering.
For our Safety-Kleen segment, competitors vary by locality and by type of service rendered, with competition coming from
Heritage-Crystal Clean and Veolia North America, along with several regional and local firms. With our Safety-Kleen Oil Plus®
