Financing Activities
Senior Secured Term Loans. On April 17, 2018, the Company, and substantially all of the Company's domestic subsidiaries as
guarantors, entered into the first amendment (the “First Amendment”) of the Term Loan Agreement. The First Amendment reduced
the applicable interest rate margin for the Company’s initial term loans (the "Term Loans") outstanding under the Term Loan
Agreement by 25 basis points for both Eurocurrency borrowings and base rate borrowings. After giving effect to the repricing, the
applicable interest rate margins for the Term Loans are 1.75% for Eurocurrency borrowings and 0.75% for base rate borrowings.
