The Company leases facilities, service centers and personal property under certain operating leases. Some of these lease
agreements contain an escalation clause for increased taxes and operating expenses and are renewable at the option of the
Company. Lease terms range from 1 to 25 years. The following is a summary of future minimum payments under operating leases
